# LCD Screen Code
This is the code for the on board LCD screen to show status of different things without getting inside the RPI directly, very useful for hardware people to trouble shoot stuff

# LCD on startup
There is a startup script that should run every time. If it doesnet try going to:
vortex-auv/scripts/
and execute script that adds our LCD screen srit into the boot-up sequence:
./vortex-auv/add_service_files_to_bootup_sequence.sh